							"contentfulId": "fO2PjkL4sIRJONVOhQKjv",
							"title": "Driving digital transformation in Healthcare",
							"eyebrow": null,
							"copy": "McKesson's US Oncology Network brings together more than 3,000 community providers and supports care for over 2.4 million patients each year. By uniting data, technology, and biopharma partnerships, the Network advances cancer research and empowers physicians to deliver world-class cancer care to local communities. To sustain this innovation securely and at scale, Cloudflare's global infrastructure and solutions—like R2 object storage—help your teams:\n\n- Protect sensitive health data across your expanding oncology and research networks with FedRAMP Moderate–authorized infrastructure. \n- Streamline collaboration to accelerate discovery and improve patient access.\n- Build a trusted digital foundation for the next generation of oncology innovation.\n",
